official_title: A bill to direct the Secretary of the Interior to transfer to John R. and Margaret J.Lowe of Big Horn County, Wyoming, certain land so as to correct an error in the patent issued to their predecessors in interest.

summary.text: Directs the Secretary of the Interior to transfer specified land in Wyoming to two named individuals to correct an error in the patent issued to their predecessors in interest in 1910.
